Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然知道變冷了 卻沒想到都結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這也別有樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:19.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:24.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 今天瀨名和安潔早上要值日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}系統的合理化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:28.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
